![Episode28.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1577206095768-G0CM39IXWTZDEDGD7ZC5/Episode28.jpg)

We are BACK. The COURT is BACK! TALON IS BACK and we hope you are too, as the guys at CBC review the second volume in Batman's new 52 continuity City of Owls. Secret societies, owl symbolism, and deadly hitmen are at every turn but can Batman turn the tide against the Court?They also get into the retcon that is New 52 Mr. Freeze!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
